{"tid":1292954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘意左個女仔…好想下次如果再有大獲野可以同佢起街一齊渡過","createTime":"2019-07-07T14:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T14:17:31.000Z","uid":211933,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e149b640d70d6e932076e92e02009c205a38a65","tid":1292954,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"呢個時期其實唔想講咁多兒女私情&hellip;<br />\n不過又有d不吐不快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個六月有開咩重要遊行69，612去到71<br />\n都係自己一個出去前線做哨兵<br />\n其實一路都見到有拍緊拖既巴絲一齊努力<br />\n覺得佢地真係好幸福&hellip;<br />\n然後每次返到屋企諗返得自己一個，身邊朋友唔願出<br />\n或者條件上無辦法可以好似自己單身寡仔咁無牽掛去做呢d野<br />\n真係有d唔開心同有d孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實宜加都有同個女仔傾計，不過覺得自己無人無物<br />\n又搵得唔多，差左7，8年有d距離，就覺得無乜信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我純粹呻下架咋，唔好意思<br />\n打後有需要到我，我都一定會再出尼做哨兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多位，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c1b8bdfc2c2900b18c9ab427d5517500d4a356","tid":1292954,"uid":27717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"同附近啲人傾計啦"},{"pid":"a2d18dbc64058f892c801a8ee22f1358b4efbc5f","tid":1292954,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"狗公"},{"pid":"98a36f77045af844d8716f0f32a44f92ed7017ed","tid":1292954,"uid":234099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"出得㴝嘅巴打，唔衰得去邊嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打要有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc09c869960a68bbcf98a2aded6bbac2c8a8265e","tid":1292954,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"